[I] Improve your pronunciation by listening to native speakers

[T] Artikulate is a pronunciation trainer that helps improving and perfecting a
[T] learner's pronunciation skills for a foreign language. It provides courses
[T] with native speaker recordings for several training languages.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/artikulate/

